---
layout: base.njk
title: AI Ops and IT Infrastructure
description: AI ops and IT infrastructure portfolio for Levi Huff. University of Cincinnati IT, graduating May 2026. Co-op experience at Tire Discounters and Total Quality Logistics.
---

<div class="bg-surface-1 text-fg-1">

  {# ── 0. Hero ─────────────────────────────────────────────────── #}
  <section id="hero" class="py-16 md:py-20">
    <div class="max-w-site mx-auto px-4 md:px-6">

      <p class="font-jb text-mono-xs tracking-[0.04em] uppercase text-amber" aria-hidden="true">&#9658; AI OPS &middot; IT INFRASTRUCTURE</p>

      <h1 class="font-syne text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold leading-[1.1] tracking-[-0.02em] text-fg-1 mt-3">
        Levi Huff
      </h1>

      <p class="font-plex text-lg text-fg-2 leading-relaxed mt-4 max-w-prose">
        I deploy AI infrastructure, run enterprise IT, and ship the software that connects them.
      </p>

      <p class="font-plex text-sm text-fg-3 mt-3 max-w-prose">
        University of Cincinnati IT, graduating {{ site.graduationDate }}. CompTIA A+ and ITF+. Network+ in progress. Co-op experience at Tire Discounters and Total Quality Logistics.
      </p>

      <div class="mt-8 flex flex-wrap gap-3">
        <a
          href="/files/resume.pdf"
          download
          class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 bg-amber hover:bg-amber-hi text-surface-0 font-plex font-semibold px-6 py-3 rounded-md shadow-d-accent transition-colors duration-[180ms] focus-visible:outline-[3px] focus-visible:outline-amber focus-visible:outline-offset-2">
          View resume
        </a>
        <a
          href="/contact/"
          class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 bg-surface-2 hover:bg-surface-3 border border-hair-1 hover:border-hair-2 text-fg-1 font-plex font-medium px-6 py-3 rounded-md transition-colors duration-[180ms] focus-visible:outline-[3px] focus-visible:outline-amber focus-visible:outline-offset-2">
          Get in touch
        </a>
      </div>

    </div>
  </section>

  {# ── 1. What I do ─────────────────────────────────────────────── #}
  <section id="what" class="py-12 md:py-16">
    <div class="max-w-site mx-auto px-4 md:px-6">

      <p class="font-jb text-mono-xs tracking-[0.04em] uppercase text-amber" aria-hidden="true">&#9658; 01 / WHAT I DO</p>
      <h2 class="font-syne text-3xl font-semibold leading-snug tracking-[-0.02em] text-fg-1 mt-2">
        Two tracks, one operator.
      </h2>

      <div class="mt-8 grid gap-4 md:grid-cols-2">

        {# IT Infrastructure card #}
        <div class="bg-surface-2 border border-hair-1 rounded-d-lg p-6 md:p-8 hover:border-hair-2 transition-colors duration-[180ms]">
          <p class="font-jb text-mono-xs tracking-[0.04em] uppercase text-fg-3">IT INFRASTRUCTURE</p>
          <h3 class="font-plex text-2xl font-semibold text-fg-1 mt-2 leading-snug">
            Operate the systems that keep an org running.
          </h3>
          <dl class="mt-6 space-y-3">
            <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row sm:items-baseline gap-1 sm:gap-3">
              <dt class="font-jb text-sm text-amber sm:w-44 shrink-0">Active Directory</dt>
              <dd class="font-plex text-base text-fg-2">domain operations and Group Policy management</dd>
            </div>
            <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row sm:items-baseline gap-1 sm:gap-3">
              <dt class="font-jb text-sm text-amber sm:w-44 shrink-0">Windows Imaging</dt>
              <dd class="font-plex text-base text-fg-2">MDT and PXE pipelines, Lenovo driver injection</dd>
            </div>
            <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row sm:items-baseline gap-1 sm:gap-3">
              <dt class="font-jb text-sm text-amber sm:w-44 shrink-0">Helpdesk Ops</dt>
              <dd class="font-plex text-base text-fg-2">ticket triage, queue ownership, multi-site support</dd>
            </div>
            <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row sm:items-baseline gap-1 sm:gap-3">
              <dt class="font-jb text-sm text-amber sm:w-44 shrink-0">Networking</dt>
              <dd class="font-plex text-base text-fg-2">CompTIA Network+ in progress, Cisco Packet Tracer labs</dd>
            </div>
          </dl>
        </div>

        {# AI Ops card #}
        <div class="bg-surface-2 border border-hair-1 rounded-d-lg p-6 md:p-8 hover:border-hair-2 transition-colors duration-[180ms]">
          <p class="font-jb text-mono-xs tracking-[0.04em] uppercase text-fg-3">AI OPS</p>
          <h3 class="font-plex text-2xl font-semibold text-fg-1 mt-2 leading-snug">
            Stand up the AI services people actually use.
          </h3>
          <dl class="mt-6 space-y-3">
            <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row sm:items-baseline gap-1 sm:gap-3">
              <dt class="font-jb text-sm text-amber sm:w-44 shrink-0">Ollama</dt>
              <dd class="font-plex text-base text-fg-2">local LLM inference, self-hosted model management</dd>
            </div>
            <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row sm:items-baseline gap-1 sm:gap-3">
              <dt class="font-jb text-sm text-amber sm:w-44 shrink-0">Containerization</dt>
              <dd class="font-plex text-base text-fg-2">Docker and Proxmox VMs for isolated, reproducible deployments</dd>
            </div>
            <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row sm:items-baseline gap-1 sm:gap-3">
              <dt class="font-jb text-sm text-amber sm:w-44 shrink-0">Local LLM Inference</dt>
              <dd class="font-plex text-base text-fg-2">self-hosted model management, API access for internal tooling</dd>
            </div>
            <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row sm:items-baseline gap-1 sm:gap-3">
              <dt class="font-jb text-sm text-amber sm:w-44 shrink-0">Observability</dt>
              <dd class="font-plex text-base text-fg-2">service health monitoring and runbook documentation</dd>
            </div>
          </dl>
        </div>

      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  {# ── 2. Tools ─────────────────────────────────────────── #}
  <section id="tools" class="py-12 md:py-16">
    <div class="max-w-site mx-auto px-4 md:px-6">

      <p class="font-jb text-mono-xs tracking-[0.04em] uppercase text-amber" aria-hidden="true">&#9658; 02 / TOOLS</p>
      <h2 class="font-syne text-3xl font-semibold leading-snug tracking-[-0.02em] text-fg-1 mt-2">
        Stack and tooling.
      </h2>
      <p class="font-plex text-lg text-fg-2 leading-relaxed mt-3 max-w-prose">
        Technologies I have deployed, maintained, or built with in production and co-op environments.
      </p>

      <div class="mt-8 grid gap-2 grid-cols-2 sm:grid-cols-3 md:grid-cols-4 lg:grid-cols-5">
        {% for tool in tools %}
        <div class="bg-surface-2 border border-hair-1 rounded-d-md p-4 hover:border-amber/[0.32] hover:-translate-y-0.5 hover:shadow-d-sm transition-[transform,border-color,box-shadow] duration-[180ms]">
          <p class="font-jb text-sm text-fg-1">{{ tool.name }}</p>
          <p class="font-jb text-mono-xs tracking-[0.04em] uppercase text-fg-4 mt-2">{{ tool.category }}</p>
        </div>
        {% endfor %}
      </div>

    </div>
  </section>

  {# ── 3. Selected work ─────────────────────────────────────────── #}
  <section id="work" class="py-12 md:py-16">
    <div class="max-w-site mx-auto px-4 md:px-6">

      <p class="font-jb text-mono-xs tracking-[0.04em] uppercase text-amber" aria-hidden="true">&#9658; 03 / WORK</p>
      <h2 class="font-syne text-3xl font-semibold leading-snug tracking-[-0.02em] text-fg-1 mt-2">
        Selected work.
      </h2>

      <div class="mt-8 grid gap-6 md:grid-cols-3">
        {% for project in projects %}
          {% if project.featured %}
            {% include "components/landing/project-card-mini.njk" %}
          {% endif %}
        {% endfor %}
      </div>

      <a
        href="/projects/"
        class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 mt-8 font-jb text-sm text-fg-2 hover:text-amber transition-colors duration-[120ms] focus-visible:outline-[3px] focus-visible:outline-amber focus-visible:outline-offset-2">
        &rarr; All projects
      </a>

    </div>
  </section>

  {# ── 4. Closing band ──────────────────────────────────────────── #}
  <section id="contact" class="border-t border-hair-1 mt-4 py-10 md:py-12">
    <div class="max-w-site mx-auto px-4 md:px-6">

      <p class="font-plex text-lg text-fg-2 max-w-prose">
        Want to talk infrastructure, AI ops, or a 2026 hire?
        <a
          href="mailto:{{ site.email }}"
          class="text-amber hover:text-amber-hi font-semibold transition-colors duration-[120ms] focus-visible:outline-[3px] focus-visible:outline-amber focus-visible:outline-offset-2">
          {{ site.email }}
        </a>
      </p>

      <div class="mt-6 flex flex-wrap gap-3">
        <a
          href="/files/resume.pdf"
          download
          class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 bg-amber hover:bg-amber-hi text-surface-0 font-plex font-semibold px-6 py-3 rounded-md shadow-d-accent transition-colors duration-[180ms] focus-visible:outline-[3px] focus-visible:outline-amber focus-visible:outline-offset-2">
          View resume
        </a>
        <a
          href="/blog/"
          class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 bg-surface-2 hover:bg-surface-3 border border-hair-1 hover:border-hair-2 text-fg-1 font-plex font-medium px-6 py-3 rounded-md transition-colors duration-[180ms] focus-visible:outline-[3px] focus-visible:outline-amber focus-visible:outline-offset-2">
          Read the blog
        </a>
      </div>

    </div>
  </section>

</div>

